---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy - abyk.online"
  description="Privacy Policy for abyk.online"
>
  
  <article class="page-container">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <p class="text-sm text-text/70 mb-8">Last updated: October 23, 2025</p>
    
    <div class="space-y-4 text-base leading-normal text-text/90">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>
        We collect minimal information necessary to provide our services. This may include:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
        <li>Usage data (pages visited, time spent)</li>
        <li>Device information (browser type, operating system)</li>
        <li>Cookies for theme preference storage</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">2. How We Use Information</h2>
      <p>
        We use the collected information to:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
        <li>Improve our website performance and user experience</li>
        <li>Understand how visitors interact with our site</li>
        <li>Remember your preferences (e.g., theme selection)</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">3. Data Storage</h2>
      <p>
        Your preferences are stored locally in your browser using localStorage.
        We do not maintain user accounts or databases in version 1 of this application.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">4. Analytics</h2>
      <p>
        We may use Vercel Analytics to collect anonymous usage statistics. This helps
        us understand traffic patterns and improve our service.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>
        This site uses Google Fonts to load the Assistant typeface. Please refer to
        Google's privacy policy for information about how they handle data.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">6. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>
        You have the right to:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
        <li>Clear your browser data at any time</li>
        <li>Disable cookies in your browser settings</li>
        <li>Request information about data we collect</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">7. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us through
        our website.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .page-container {
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
